data.name: pl_google_sitemaps_show_hidden.Help
data.value: Select whether the Google Sitemaps will include hidden tabs.

data.name: pl_google_sitemaps_show_disabled.Help
data.value: Select whether the Google Sitemaps will include disabled tabs.

data.name: pl_google_sitemaps_index_non_public.Help
data.value: Select whether the Google Sitemaps will include tabs that are not visible to the general public. This option should be left disabled unless you are creating a sitemap for a Google Search Appliance.

data.name: pl_google_sitemaps_use_per_page.Help
data.value: Select whether Google Sitemaps priority will use per-page priority settings in DNN 05.01.00+. If 'Yes' is selected, the priority of each page must be specified individually. If this setting is set to 'Yes' then you must adjust each page's priority individually. This setting is ignored in versions of DNN prior to 05.01.00.
